Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.88,0:49:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But I think malice malice\Nuh
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.64,0:49:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,f false uh uh\Naccusations against your your fellow man
