Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.24,0:49:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing is to learn how to transcend\Nthem. And the way to transcend it is to
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.35,0:49:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,see that everything is only being what\Nit can be. And if it could be something
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.28,0:50:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,else, it would be. Therefore, to be\Nuh accepting of everything as it is, as
