Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.76,0:50:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,karma then the world is perfect as it\Nis. So let's ask the arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:53.11,0:50:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The world is perfect as it is. The world\Nis perfect as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.59,0:51:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise me you will stop trying to\Nchange the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.88,0:51:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Why? Because if you take away from me\Nthe chance to learn that this is the
