Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.24,0:53:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here because We're here because\Nwe're here. We're here because we're
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.16,0:53:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,here because we're here because we're\Nhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.35,0:53:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here because we're here. All\Nright, we are going to pick up where we
