Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.20,0:54:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Andromeda is a camel, isn't it?\NPractical spirituality.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.07,0:54:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, starts out with goodwill.\Nfor those who deserve it. Of course,
