Dialogue: 0,0:56:41.68,0:56:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not good, good or better. It's just\Nthe way it is. So how it is is how it
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.72,0:56:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is.\NEverything is what it is. That's the
