Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.24,0:57:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that's what it means to be a\Nfoot. You say, "Oh, that's what it means
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.96,0:57:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a foot." Thank you, foot, for\Ntelling me what you are. What everything
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.52,0:57:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,means is what it is.\NWhat it means is what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.20,0:57:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That prevents intellectual rambling.\Nlooking for significances and hidden
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.40,0:57:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,meanings.\NAll right. So, practical spirituality is
